Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:00.42,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:120420,120420}Practice for "The Smile of Stone," the play that will decide the future of Tsukikage Theater, has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:04.52,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:124524,124524}Maya's role is a doll who doesn't move at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:08.19,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:128194,128194}She tries to conceptualize its movements by putting bamboo sticks around her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:12.26,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:132265,132265}However, around that time, her mother Haru's condition was getting worse and worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:27.06,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141141,147064}{\an5\pos(766,750)\fscy95\blur1\fad(800,800)}—Episode 15—\NWelcome to\NThe Underground Theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152652,152652}Look at this huge advertisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155221,155221}It's put on by Orion Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157357,157357}Their first day is our first day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160994,160994}It will be pretty tough for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162796,162796}And where is our theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165298,165298}The basement of that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168968,168968}There?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170603,170603}We are going to play in the basement of that building?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173206,173206}Basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174474,174474}It used to be a cafe,\Nbut it went out of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:02:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179612,179612}No wonder it went out of business…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181448,181448}Don't complain.\NWe got this place for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184284,184284}Oh, it's dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184651,184651}Do you smell the dampness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187587,187587}Creepy…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190790,190790}The outside is pretty bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193193,193193}It's even worse inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194994,194994}I'm not sure if we can make this place pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199065,199065}Welcome to our underground theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204738,204738}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205905,205905}This is our, {\i1}our{\i0} theater here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208908,208908}That's right.\NLet's make it look nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211378,211378}Let's clean it up.\NWe can make this a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213413,213413}This is our home sweet home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215815,215815}Remodeling is up to us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218351,218351}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220687,220687}Hey, let's get to work now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222589,222589}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228661,228661}Look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230830,230830}I wonder why the hell they opened up a theater there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234000,234000}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235301,235301}What happened to the fame of our theater, the Orion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237837,237837}Well, we'll get all of the audience here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240407,240407}They'll go out of business soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242442,242442}I wonder if that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246746,246746}Ms. Himekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248014,248014}I just dropped by to see the practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251651,251651}You all, you shouldn't underestimate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254621,254621}But, neither Ikkakuju Theater\Nnor Tsukikage Theater is very popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259192,259192}They are not even on our level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261261,261261}Besides, they are not equipped well either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268134,268134}Do you know about Kitajima Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269002,269002}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270403,270403}She's the girl on the truck.\NHarada Kikuko called her a "stage storm."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274307,274307}"Stage storm?"\NBy Harada Kikuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276476,276476}We can finally practice, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279212,279212}She is the stage storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281481,281481}You should be careful not to have her storm Orion Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295695,295695}Whew, we're finally done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:04:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298331,298331}Good work.\NWe have some coffee inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301134,301134}Do we have everything we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303870,303870}Yup.\NEverything is sold as is though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306639,306639}Oh?\NIt's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308842,308842}We're lucky we're done carrying everything inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310977,310977}Maya, come on in.\NYou'll get wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314581,314581}{\i1}Rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322455,322455}The umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330230,330230}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330497,330497}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331798,331798}Excuse me, is Sakurakōji in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333733,333733}Sakurakōji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335335,335335}Hey, that's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337037,337037}Oh, the one from the donut shop…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339673,339673}…who's with different girls all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342275,342275}Sakurakōji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343777,343777}You be careful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345245,345245}He's become much of a playboy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348882,348882}Playboy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351017,351017}I'm so glad Sakurakōji\Nis asking us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354854,354854}Everyone,\Neat whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356856,356856}It's all on me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:05:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358525,358525}– Really? Thank you.\N– Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362529,362529}What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364097,364097}You'll brew it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364831,364831}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366166,366166}No, your girlfriend will get upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368668,368668}You have one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374007,374007}Of course you do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375842,375842}Yeah, used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378211,378211}What?\NThen, not anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380814,380814}Wow, can I put my name on the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382549,382549}No!\NLet me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383850,383850}Well, sure, okay!\NWhy not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389055,389055}{\i1}Yeah. It's a thing of the past.\NI should put it behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402802,402802}Maya!\NMaya, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417817,417817}{\i1}Why did I even run after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:06:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419953,419953}{\i1}I had just decided to put all this behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423590,423590}{\i1}I had so many things\NI wanted to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425959,425959}{\i1}But now it's all gone…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429529,429529}{\i1}He's doing fine without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433800,433800}{\i1}I might have just been one of those many girls of his after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441741,441741}I'm here to give you your umbrella back. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443943,443943}You didn't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453286,453286}Let me walk you to the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462395,462395}{\i1}There are so many things\NI wanted to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468568,468568}{\i1}No words can come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472639,472639}Bye, Sakurakōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475108,475108}Uhh, Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475575,475575}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477310,477310}You did great in\N"Wuthering Heights."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479546,479546}Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481681,481681}But, I'm not Heathcliff,\Nunfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487354,487354}Sakurakōji…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491658,491658}{\i1}He is as nice as he used to be,\Nbut something is different…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:19.79,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:499799,499799}Manpuku Ken
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507807,507807}Haru, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510410,510410}I'm sorry for causing so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513113,513113}Well, we wanted to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517751,517751}How about going…\Nto a rest home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523423,523423}We hate to do this,\Nbut we are in the food business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527727,527727}We cannot keep a sick person\Nin here like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530563,530563}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532232,532232}You are not going to get better\Njust laying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535168,535168}Then you might as well\Nconcentrate on resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:08:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539205,539205}Maya will be very worried\Nonce she hears about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543977,543977}She is concentrating so much on acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550984,550984}The best thing for you is to get better soon, and then come back and work for us again before Maya gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560026,560026}Thank you so much for all of your help for such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563997,563997}Then, it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567634,567634}{\i1}Maya, Maya… Where are you and what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:36.10,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:576109,576109}In the basement of what used to be a cafe, the practice of "The Smile of Stone" heated up every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582415,582415}It's ridiculous to brush her hair everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591358,591358}{\i1}I'm getting the movement of a doll down little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600667,600667}This is a hard role for Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602569,602569}Yeah, she's on the stage constantly, but allowed no movement at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605005,605005}No, what I mean is the time she has to sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609476,609476}Just look at her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614114,614114}{\i1}Sakurakōji, what changed you so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618251,618251}{\i1}I didn't know that it hurts so bad\Nto have someone you love leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623890,623890}{\i1}Mother! Besides, I haven't\Neven called her once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629829,629829}{\i1}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632999,632999}{\i1}No, I didn't\Neven think about her…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637203,637203}{\i1}Not once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641641,641641}{\i1}I miss you, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645145,645145}Miss Tsukikage would have done the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647313,647313}Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648815,648815}Are you out of your mind?\NThinking about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651985,651985}A doll doesn't have any emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655455,655455}Doesn't have any emotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656956,656956}That's right.\NNothing in its head, nor in its heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660060,660060}That's what a doll is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668601,668601}You want to learn\Nthe emotion of a doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671271,671271}Yes, I think\NI'm learning the movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674307,674307}But I can't stop thinking\Nwhen I'm just sitting around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682115,682115}You should go visit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684017,684017}Sansōji Shrine?\NIn Saitama Prefecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686086,686086}Yes, go there and learn\Nhow to kill your own emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690557,690557}Kill my emotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692559,692559}He can teach you\Nthe emotion of a doll there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:40.80,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:700800,700800}Sansōji
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703870,703870}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704504,704504}Look how old it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706539,706539}I wonder what she wants me to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708541,708541}You are about to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710543,710543}Are you the ones\Nthat Miss Tsukikage sent to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713313,713313}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715548,715548}Then hurry up and come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726526,726526}He seems pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728595,728595}I wonder what relationship\Nhe has with Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731197,731197}Miss Tsukikage stayed here\Nfor a while in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735702,735702}He heard us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736936,736936}Miss Tsukikage…\NIt has been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740340,740340}Okay, please get into the pose of zazen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743943,743943}Zazen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745712,745712}Yes. This is a temple of Zen.\NZen means no mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748848,748848}Look what we got ourselves into.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753920,753920}{\i1}Maya, did you forget about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757991,757991}{\i1}But I haven't forgotten you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760260,760260}{\i1}I will live until the day\NI see you again.
Comment: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:55.77,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:775775,775775}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:59.52,0:12:59.52,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:779529,779529}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:02.44,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:782448,782448}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794894,794894}Here, straighten up your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797597,797597}It's hard to achieve emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800433,800433}There are many minds around,\Nbut look at the stone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805271,805271}There are no minds in stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808875,808875}Forget that you are a human being,\Nand become a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813813,813813}Then you will be free from your mind and you will achieve the expression of emptiness on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821688,821688}{\i1}Think I am a stone\Nand become… a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829329,829329}A stone doesn't think about\NSakurakōji, nor about mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834334,834334}{\i1}Become a stone…\NBecome a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840540,840540}{\i1}Maya, it's been two years\Nsince you left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844411,844411}{\i1}I bet you grew a little, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846613,846613}{\i1}I have cried many times that I don't need you anymore, but I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850750,850750}{\i1}After all, you are the only daughter I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856690,856690}Excuse me, but your magazine…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862696,862696}This is… Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865098,865098}"Natsu Eriko's acting in this play was great, but Kitajima Maya, who played the childhood Catherine, did a fantastic job, doing almost as well as Natsu's role as Catherine."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875408,875408}Maya, this is Maya.\NMy daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878411,878411}Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880647,880647}My daughter was in a play\Nwith Natsu Eriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887487,887487}I can't be sitting\Nlike this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889689,889689}Ladies and gentlemen,\N"The Smile of Stone" will open today at 6:30 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894027,894027}It starts at 6:30 PM.\NDon't miss out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:54.79,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:894794,894794}The Smile of Stone\NTsukikage and Ikkakuju Theaters
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900500,900500}They'll open today too, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902902,902902}Look at them. They look like they are trying to draw customers into a cabaret or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905638,905638}What can they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906906,906906}We have "Hamlet" and they have "The Smile of Stone," which is totally unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912512,912512}Well, we'll see how many people they can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915448,915448}It starts at 6:30 PM.\NDon't miss out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919085,919085}Is it selling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920720,920720}Not at all.\NOnly four of them so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923256,923256}Four?\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925091,925091}Can I get one, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926659,926659}Yes, yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929095,929095}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931865,931865}Himekawa Ayumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934200,934200}I am looking forward\Nto seeing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936102,936102}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939906,939906}Look how dirty it is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941741,941741}Told you we should have gone\Nto see "Hamlet."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944144,944144}What could have I done?\NIt was all sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948648,948648}Everyone else here is doing the same:\Nkilling time because they couldn't get a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955055,955055}Hey, isn't that…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957924,957924}…Himekawa Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960827,960827}What is Himekawa Ayumi\Ndoing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964831,964831}Hey, isn't that the guy who played\NHeathcliff in "Wuthering Heights?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966800,966800}Majima Ryo, I think his name was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:10.47,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:970470,970470}Majima Ryo had appeared to see\Nthe remembrance of Catherine…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:13.97,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:973973,973973}…not being able to forget Maya's Catherine in "Wuthering Heights."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977911,977911}Wow, we have two starts here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980880,980880}Huh, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981348,981348}It's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983049,983049}No, I can't see Ms. Himekawa anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985885,985885}The plane is shaking due to turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990190,990190}Please wear your seat belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002168,1002168}I am Prefew, an attorney. I heard you called for me. What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:45.97,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1005972,1005972}"The Smile of Stone"\Nhas opened its curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:48.97,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1008975,1008975}After that, the scene continued with Marisa Parsoromeo, a girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014381,1014381}…who has lost her parents in a plane crash, giving her will to her attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021821,1021821}Thank you for gathering here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025291,1025291}My name is Prefew, an attorney…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025592,1025592}{\i1}Where is Kitajima Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029262,1029262}{\i1}That's Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032832,1032832}Maya is playing a doll. Why?\NWhat's her goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036836,1036836}That's Catherine?\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039439,1039439}{\i1}Ayumi?\NAyumi is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042175,1042175}{\i1}Mr. Majima, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043710,1043710}…there are two wills from Marisa here.\NMay I open them now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047013,1047013}Hello, everyone!\NHow do you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052952,1052952}Whoa, who is that?\NHow good looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057023,1057023}Then I will open the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062262,1062262}Marisa Parsoromeo.\NLeave all my belongings to my loving doll, Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072605,1072605}That's a huge doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074908,1074908}No, silly!\NThat's a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076509,1076509}Oh, you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:17:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077944,1077944}{\i1}Prohibited from any facial expression, movement, or words, she's not supposed to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083917,1083917}{\i1}That's a hard role.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085452,1085452}Catherine, where have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088021,1088021}This is so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089889,1089889}My weekly salary is only 2.50 pounds, and this doll is worth 65 million pounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096830,1096830}I have to clean her up everyday like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100500,1100500}How crazy is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105972,1105972}Here, stay put.\NI have to go clean up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112412,1112412}{\i1}The doll is the key to the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114547,1114547}{\i1}If there's any movement that lets people know that it's a human,\Nthe play is all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119552,1119552}{\i1}Miss Tsukikage sure did bet on her,\Nand she is doing fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125158,1125158}{\i1}Kitajima Maya… What a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127594,1127594}{\i1}This is Kitajima Maya,\Nwho wears a mask of a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130964,1130964}{\i1}There's no trace of the Catherine who gave me passion and kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135602,1135602}{\i1}How silly was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138304,1138304}{\i1}I was an actor myself, and I fell in love with Maya who wore a mask of Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146346,1146346}Good bye, my Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:15.55,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1155555,1155555}The play, which started with an audience of twelve, ended in a big success.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165532,1165532}My prince Rei… I'm in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168234,1168234}I shouldn't have let her see…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173173,1173173}Please, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175442,1175442}Poor people.\NThe game is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179212,1179212}Poor people?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182882,1182882}Yes, the people of Orion Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194561,1194561}Look at that, all sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196029,1196029}That's how a theater should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201134,1201134}Hey, did you think the audience enjoyed it a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204170,1204170}Yeah, there weren't too many,\Nbut it was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207474,1207474}Those girls went crazy over Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209142,1209142}Yeah, they were like, "Mr. Rei…"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211311,1211311}No one noticed that you are a woman, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214314,1214314}Hey, watch your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216182,1216182}Oh, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216850,1216850}Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218985,1218985}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220320,1220320}I'm done with the backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221955,1221955}When I get you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224958,1224958}I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225792,1225792}Lord have mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233366,1233366}What are you doing,\Nall smiling like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236436,1236436}We are all here as one.\NI like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239806,1239806}That's right.\NThat's why the play went so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242676,1242676}When everyone's heart beats\Nthe same pace, there's born a great play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247380,1247380}Also, it's important for an actor to pace\Nthe heartbeat with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253219,1253219}Pace the heartbeat\Nwith the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:20:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258758,1258758}{\i1}I have never thought of it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262662,1262662}{\i1}I only thought of acting for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281381,1281381}{\i1}That's right, I have never thought of anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285318,1285318}{\i1}I always focused on just myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288888,1288888}{\i1}I just played at my own pace on all the other plays I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294661,1294661}{\i1}Maya, learn how to kill your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301634,1301634}{\i1}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303103,1303103}{\i1}That's why Miss Tsukikage\Ngave me the role of a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306673,1306673}{\i1}To empty myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1311378,1311378}I wonder what happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313213,1313213}Seems like she's learning\Nanother step about acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316583,1316583}Act to kill her own emotions…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:21:59.35,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1319352,1319352}The Smile of Stone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:03.12,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1323123,1323123}The word about "The Smile of Stone" spread, and the number in the audience grew as the days passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:15.20,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1335201,1335201}And, ten days later…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1338138,1338138}Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339739,1339739}Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1346112,1346112}T-This can't be…
Comment: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:50.36,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1370369,1370369}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:03.79,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1377669,1383799}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.79,0:23:09.88,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1383799,1389889}{\blur3}…and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.88,0:23:21.89,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1389889,1401899}{\blur3}Somewhere calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:34.03,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1401899,1414039}{\blur3}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:39.91,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1414039,1419919}{\blur3}…more surer than words…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:46.04,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1419919,1426049}{\blur3}…telling us gently…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.04,0:23:52.13,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1426049,1432139}{\blur3}…that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.13,0:23:58.22,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1432139,1438229}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:04.23,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1438229,1444239}{\blur3}…for the dream\Non my cheek…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.23,0:24:10.19,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1444239,1450199}{\blur3\fad(0,500)}…belongs to you.
